Check out my new video with leading climate scientist Johan Rockström and the Potsdam Institute for Climate Impact Research on the third topic: How can we stabilize our climate? Let me know your thoughts below! 🙏

#Sustainability #Environment #ClimateChange

node.text:
New launch at the #LondonEPrix ⚡ Welcome to the @heineken #GreenerBar...an event concept to save more than:

🗑️ 6,500 kg of waste – the equivalent to the daily waste from 2,200 average households!

⚡ 5,300 kilowatt-hours of energy – equivalent to run over 4,300 dishwasher cycles!

🌎 21,000 kilograms of CO2 emissions – equivalent to driving a fossil fuel vehicle around a Formula E track 7,775 times! 

💧 25,000 litres of water – equivalent to over 53,000 pints of water!

A completely new entertainment experience that uses new building methods, materials and technologies focused on improving how we up-cycle, recycle and reuse materials, to create a completely circular environment, and step towards our ambition to make event bars a little bit greener. Cheers 🙏
